@startuml
title Use Case: File Evidence

actor "Officer" as O
actor "Evidence Clerk" as EC
actor "Detective" as DE
actor "Lab Technician" as LT

usecase "File Evidence" as UC

O --> UC : collects & submits
EC --> UC : processes & stores
DE --> UC : requests for case
LT --> UC : analyzes evidence

UC .> (Tag Evidence) : include
UC .> (Document Chain) : include
UC .> (Store Securely) : include
UC .> (Update Records) : include

UC <.. (Send to Lab) : extend <<if analysis needed>>
UC <.. (Present in Court) : extend <<if trial evidence>>
UC <.. (Destroy Evidence) : extend <<if court ordered>>

note right of UC
  Maintains chain of custody
  Ensures evidence integrity
  Critical for court admissibility
  Legal requirements strict
end note
@enduml
